comments: Introductory level knowledge of Middle Egyptian language and grammar.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Very well structured and thorough instruction of the language. Incredibly accessible professor. Really enjoyed the course overall.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I highly, highly recommend this class to anyone interested in learning hieroglyphs!

Definitely take it if you're very interested in learning Hieroglyphics, especially if you have a background in/plan to study Egyptology. If you're only idly interested the workload and heavy grammar focus may be a turn off.
